2. **Frame Extraction**: Extract frames from the video at regular intervals (e.g., every second or every half-second) to ensure you capture all potential appearances of men.
3. **Object Detection**: Use an object detection model to identify and count the number of men in each frame. This can be done using pre-trained models like YOLO, SSD, or a custom model trained on human detection.
